# BFF — Health Checks (M17-S04)
# /health/live is a pure process-up check — always 200, no dependencies.
# /health/ready checks the backend's /health/live (2s timeout) — 503 when the backend
# is unreachable. Both routes are @Public() (bypass JwtAuthGuard/TenantGuard/ActiveStaffGuard).

### GET /v1/health/live — always 200
GET {{bffUrl}}/v1/health/live

###

### GET /v1/health/ready — 200 when the backend is reachable, 503 otherwise
GET {{bffUrl}}/v1/health/ready

###
